@86 = ~Ring of Invisibility
 'The Thieves Escape'
This ring once belonged to a Calimshan Sea Captain called Josan Paris. A talented Seaman Josan captained a large warship out of Memnon whose purpose was to free the Shining Sea of pirates. The ring was retrieved from a pirate ship and Josan kept it as a token. When he discovered its ability for invisibility he turned his profession into a more opportunistic one eventually becoming the kind of pirate he once pursued.  

